# Task Manager Backend API

## Overview

This project is a **RESTful backend API for a Task Manager application**.
It supports user authentication, role-based access control, and CRUD operations for tasks.

The API is built using **Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB**, and secured with **JWT authentication**.

---

## Tech Stack

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB + Mongoose
* JWT Authentication
* bcryptjs (Password Hashing)
* express-validator (Input Validation)
* Swagger (API Documentation)

---

## Features

* User registration and login
* Password hashing with bcrypt
* JWT based authentication
* Role based authorization (User / Admin)
* CRUD operations for tasks
* Input validation middleware
* Global error handling
* API versioning (`/api/v1`)
* Swagger API documentation

